name: A New Thing
description:
This work is a representation of me when I do a new thing in a new world. 

Since I joined and started the NFT path, I have learned a lot of good things in this community, like fun interactions, motivation to improve my work, and support from fellow artists and collectors who keep the community growing.

Seeing many artists with great works is a motivation to improve my work.

I also learned that consistency is matters. Hard work, dedication, and consistency will bring success in what we do.

When we start a new thing, keep learning and do it consistently. We're All Gonna Make It. LFG!
